      "page_number": 1,
      "raw_text": "LA GRANDE. Ore. April s.-The\nland Office announces that $4,000\nacres in northwestern Baker county\nwill be thrown open for homestead\nentry this spring. This land, COM\nprising portions of three townships.\nlies along the Snake river in town.\nships 8 and Z. range 4S. and township\nin range Al. There are now few\nsQuatters on the land, probably not\nover 20 families in ALL Many streams\nflow each way from the intersecting\ndivides."
    }
